data.description:
This beautiful New Construction home will have three bedrooms and two and a half baths.  The floor plan will feature a foyer, separate dining area, a large panty and a master bathroom that has his/her sinks.

This home will have a two car garage with side entrance.  The front view will have a grand entry with an open gable and wooden beams.

***Half bath shown in floor plan is a $2500 option.  The home will have a larger laundry and closet if the half bath option is not picked before start of construction.***
